            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <AlertCircle className="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Driving Style</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Aggressive acceleration and hard braking waste energy. Smooth driving improves range by 5-10%.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Card>

      <Card className="p-6 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 border-2 border-green-400">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
