            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>

        <!-- Factor 2: AC Usage -->
        <Card className="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg flex items-center gap-2">
              <Wind className="h-5 w-5 text-cyan-600" />
              2. Air Conditioning Usage
            </h3>
            <Badge className="bg-yellow-200 text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-400">Moderate Impact</Badge>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              AC compressor uses battery power. Impact varies by outside temperature and AC setting.
            </p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold mb-2">Range Reduction:</p>
                <ul class="ml-4 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Mild weather (20-25¬∞C):</strong> 5-8% reduction</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Hot summer (35-40¬∞C):</strong> 12-15% reduction</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>AC off completely:</strong> Maximum range</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Fan only (no cooling):</strong> 2-3% reduction</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold mb-2">For Pune-Mumbai Trip:</p>
                <ul class="ml-4 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Without AC: ~140 kWh used (35% battery)</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ With AC: ~155 kWh used (39% battery)</li>
